## 基于Centos系统安装docker

1、卸载旧版docker
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# yum remove docker \
>                   docker-client \
>                   docker-client-latest \
>                   docker-common \
>                   docker-latest \
>                   docker-latest-logrotate \
>                   docker-logrotate \
>                   docker-engine
```

2、使用存储库安装
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# yum install -y yum-utils
[root@Centos8 ~]# yum-config-manager \
>     --add-repo \
>     https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo
```

3、安装docker引擎
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# yum install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io
```

4、启动docker
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# systemctl start docker
```

5、设置开机启动docker
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# systemctl enable docker
```

6、测试docker是否安装成功
```bash
[root@Centos8 ~]# docker -v
[root@Centos8 ~]# docker info
```
